---
title: Maple-Bacon Bison Burgers with Potato Wedges and Dijonnaise
description: Maple syrup-glazed bacon on top of a bison burger just screams Canada, eh? We've paired it with sharp old cheddar, some vinegary greens and cheesy Parm wedges – plus, a mayo dipper!
